{"tid":767852,"cid":4,"subCid":0,"title":"NOKIA次季出貨量暴增7.82倍　重返全球前十","createTime":"2018-08-05T01:59:06.000Z","updateTime":"2018-08-17T00:53:42.000Z","uid":22675,"like":52,"dislike":4,"uniUserReply":25,"replies":[{"pid":"8641478cfc89a390a0ad80ababda0dcc98e90657","tid":767852,"uid":22675,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-08-05T01:59:06.000Z","msg":"08月04日(六) 17:58   <br />\n<img src=\"http://hk.on.cc/hk/bkn/cnt/finance/20180804/photo/bkn-20180804175800526-0804_00842_001_01p.jpg?20180804194442\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fhk.on.cc%2Fhk%2Fbkn%2Fcnt%2Ffinance%2F20180804%2Fphoto%2Fbkn-20180804175800526-0804_00842_001_01p.jpg%3F20180804194442&h=33114f2f&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\nHMD接手諾基亞品牌後，今年次季重新打入全球出貨量第九位。（互聯網）<br />\n<br />\n國際調查機構CounterPoint統計報告顯示，相比起去年同期，今年第二季全球智能電話出貨量總體呈現小幅度下滑趨勢，出貨量排行榜前五名是三星、華為、蘋果公司(Apple Inc.)、小米、OPPO等。 <br />\n<br />\n然而，在Top 10名單當中有一個十分亮眼的品牌&mdash;&mdash;HMD，即諾基亞品牌的授權商，現今再次打入排名前十，今年次季排全球第九位，期內出貨量按年勁升782% 。相比起去年的50萬部，今年第二季Nokia的全球出貨量逆勢上升至450萬部。 <br />\n<br />\n相反，曾經同期發家共成長的品牌如索尼、HTC，現今郤已經不見踪影。"},{"pid":"aa37184d918735fba47a03781852ef215f97336b","tid":767852,"uid":132587,"like":8,"dislike":37,"score":-29,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-08-05T02:17:26.000Z","msg":"出貨量多唔代表多人買<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"724bc169bfe40981f9493619bdab2804d2c42382","tid":767852,"uid":23677,"like":6,"dislike":1,"score":5,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-08-05T03:19:28.000Z","msg":"舊年第二季有幾多部nokia 機呀? <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n你拎舊年同今年機海去比, 出貨量唔多就奇啦"},{"pid":"bb11ccad9363d0974dd2630831b5b6047da72e50","tid":767852,"uid":17765,"like":31,"dislike":4,"score":27,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2018-08-05T03:20:20.000Z","msg":"幾時Nokia Motorola 呢啲上返世界頭三？<br />\n見到啲抄嚟抄去做爛市支那垃圾喺度破壞哂成個電話市場<br />\n真係火都嚟"},{"pid":"c70a7dcfde4e05c66b779ca4e22994064dcbf972","tid":767852,"uid":23677,"like":5,"dislike":1,"score":4,"quote":{"pid":"bb11ccad9363d0974dd2